---
title: Smoky Beyond Meat® Cheeseburgers with Caramelized Onions
description: This classic diner meal becomes next-level delicious with the addition of smoky flavours courtesy of smoked paprika and garlic! Topped with caramelized onions, these Beyond Meat® burgers are sure to earn a place among your family’s favourites
